{"tid":658702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港創新科技專才】陳易希會考僅得12分","createTime":"2018-05-09T08:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T08:15:08.000Z","uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d314b997e110cf697c6ccb07b6acd1c1f209a92","tid":658702,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"應屆會考生陳易希獲科大破格取錄，他在會考僅得十二分，他今日多謝科大能夠做到「求學不是求分數」。<br />\n<br />\n有小發明家之稱的陳易希出席一項公開活動時承認，在應屆中學會考取得十二分，部分成績有B和C，但未有說明是哪一科最佳，他承認有需要改善語文程度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20070226130354/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/060821/12/1rplf.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20070226130354%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F060821%2F12%2F1rplf.html&d=Wasgvqq%2BsjEdEnWNDSVYoEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=29cd1272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20070226130354/http://hk.news.yahoo.com/060821/12/1rplf.html</a>"},{"pid":"f4692601fd3c6b264f5b2a9f01af4353b91efa92","tid":658702,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"新民黨成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}